    "algorithm_path": "medication-path",
    "algorithm_path_description": "Patients with PPI medication orders (Paths A and C). Captures both diagnosed GERD patients and the very large Path C population — PPIs are arguably the most cross-prescribed drug class (dyspepsia, NSAID-associated gastritis, H. pylori eradication, prophylaxis in critically ill, empirical relief of upper GI symptoms).",
